messages.content: ComfyUI-HF is a ComfyUI node that allows users to work with Hugging Face repositories.
Which node in ComfyUI-HF is used to generate prompts using GPT2 models?
The GPT2Node in ComfyUI-HF is used to load the given GPT2 model to generate prompts.
Which model is trained on Midjourney prompts?
The succinctly/text2image-prompt-generator model (~600mb) is trained on Midjourney prompts.
Is there a model finetuned using prompts from lexica.art?
Yes, the AUTOMATIC/promptgen-lexart model (~300mb) is finetuned using 134,819 prompts from lexica.art.
Which model uses prompts from majinai.art and is NSFW?
The AUTOMATIC/promptgen-majinai-unsafe model (~300mb) uses 825 prompts from majinai.art and is not safe for work (NSFW).
Is there a model that uses prompts from majinai.art and is safe for work?
Yes, the AUTOMATIC/promptgen-majinai-safe model (~300mb) uses 1,654 prompts from majinai.art and is safe for work.
Which is the largest model listed for generating stable diffusion prompts?
The largest model listed for generating stable diffusion prompts is Ar4ikov/gpt2-medium-650k-stable-diffusion-prompt-generator (~1.4gb).
